    "long_instructions": "#### will.i.am's \"I Like to Move It\" \r\n\r\nRecreate this portion of the song using will.i.am's **algorithm** below:\r\n\r\n1) First play the Bass and the Kick together\r\n2) Then add in the Percussion Kick\r\n3) Repeat Step 2\r\n4) Then add in the Percussion Beat\r\n\r\nFollow this **algorithm** to recreate this intro! Your code should sound like the example below!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/ee7f83ef0bb1c4e3c0bc439b899e7164-image-1745350282096.png)",
